                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820220-58-defend631 t17820220-58-punish275"></join>
               To raise gravel three years on the river Thames
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried before Mr. Justice GOULD.</p>
